description:
This model is an RDN model trained from the repo https://github.com/idealo/image-super-resolution.
The dataset used for training is DIV2K (https://data.vision.ee.ethz.ch/cvl/DIV2K/).
The model's scale is 3x, and the model's hyperparameters are: {C: 3, D: 10, G: 64, G0: 64 }.
The model is quantized to 8 bits.
